OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779869194
OL,3,CSpectators injured after motorbike
OL,4,Ccrash during TT practice on the Isle
OL,5,Cof Man
OL,7,FA serious incident involving
OL,8,Fspectators being injured forced Isle
OL,9,Fof Man TT organisers to suspend all
OL,10,Factivity during a practice session.
OL,12,FEight spectators were transferred to
OL,13,FNobles Hospital for further assessment
OL,14,Fand treatment, including the rider.
OL,16,FAll spectators were reported as
OL,17,F'conscious', and were transferred to
OL,18,FNobles Hospital for further assessment
OL,19,Fand treatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
