OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779869194
OL,3,CSpectators injured after motorbike
OL,4,Ccrash during TT practice on the Isle
OL,5,Cof Man
OL,7,FThe session was immediately stopped
OL,8,Fand all racing activity around the
OL,9,FMountain Course was suspended to allow
OL,10,Ffor emergency services to respond.
OL,12,FAn investigative process is now
OL,13,Funderway involving race, medical and
OL,14,Fsafety personnel.
OL,16,FThe Isle of Man TT is set to continue
OL,17,Ftomorrow with a further practice
OL,18,Fsession due to begin at 18:30.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
